        title: 'Complex Medical Treatments in Istanbul: Cancer, Transplant & IVF Guide',
        meta_title: 'Cancer Treatment, Organ Transplant & IVF Istanbul — NodensCare',
        meta_description: 'YMYL-compliant guide to complex medical treatments in Istanbul: oncology, organ transplant, IVF with PGD/PGS. JCI hospitals, professor-led multidisciplinary teams.',
